name: Feeder
description:
yesterday (aug 30th 2021) i changed my username to bruhweegi... cant edit the game until the brackeys game jam voting is over in 12 days... so thats why it says "art, code and audio by bruhvioli" (my old username) lol

as bruhweegi your goal is to feed bruhtilta until she stops chasing you while watching out for walls of glass and explosives. BRUHTILDA USES ALL OF HER SENSES TO ATTACK YOU AND IT IS VERY CHAOTIC SO GET READY FOR SOME TRYHARDING!!

A BRACKEYS / SENSORY OVERLOAD GAME JAM SUBMISSION!!!

i live streamed some of the development here :)  https://www.twitch.tv/bruhvioli

pro tip: the bombs, walls and stuns always appear in the same order, only the x position is randomized.
